Class LockStatus

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DomainEntity, EntityObject, java.io.Serializable

    public class LockStatus
extends AbstractChangeableEntity
implements java.io.Serializable
    The LockStatus is a POJO that defines an entity for lock_status table in Ephesoft DB. This domain object is used for handling the locking capability for different feature of Ephesoft.

    3.0
